          <p>I am a certified English-language copyeditor and copywriter with years of experience in meeting a wide range of content needs, from writing articles, blog posts, and commercial/personal websites to editing full-length novels and children's chapter books. I believe in delivering quality text content minus the hair-pulling (because who can afford a bad hair day?).</p>
